name: hyppo
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "hyppo" %}
{% set version = "0.3.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/hyppo-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1c3b830dca2792a621bbe06ce215200884685068f60de29c5c521493ae61eaf3

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - autograd >=1.3
    - numba >=0.46
    - numpy >=1.17
    - python >=3.6
    - scikit-learn >=0.19.1
    - scipy >=1.4.0

test:
  imports:
    - hyppo
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://hyppo.neurodata.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/neurodata/hyppo
  summary: A comprehensive independence testing package
  license: MIT
  license_file:
    - LICENSE.md

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - thewchan
